org.eclipse.jst.jsf.facesconfig.emf
Interface NavigationRuleType

All Known Implementing Classes:
NavigationRuleTypeImpl
public interface NavigationRuleType

A representation of the model object 'Navigation Rule Type'.

The following features are supported:

  • Description
  • Display Name
  • Icon
  • From View Id
  • Navigation Case
  • Navigation Rule Extension
  • Id

See Also:
